table, mutes the microphone, and once it is being picked up again it unmutes the microphone. In addition to that, custom events can be programmed, e.g., to pause and to continue the recording.<\/p>","text_size_desktop":15,"text_size_mobile":14,"color_text":"#4d4d4f","button_text":"","button_link":"","show_separator":true,"color_title":"#eaeaea","image_gap":0}}},"block_order":["b4cae6fc-4541-4ed9-975f-4d9076f9548a"],"settings":{"show_section_margin":false,"top-margin-desktop":30,"bottom-margin-desktop":30,"top-margin-mobile":20,"bottom-margin-mobile":20,"show_section_top_margin":false,"section-top-margin-desktop":80,"section-top-margin-mobile":50}},"142f6f24-1302-4356-9950-f7a6168e7cdd":{"type":"custom-image-with-text","blocks":{"c6d1e0d8-3dbf-41d2-8f35-2b2d239ebbe4":{"type":"Image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/csm_smp4000_lossless-voice-technology_fim_rgb_3cf3c94c1f-transformed_700x_aa04b893-c154-4dae-ad2a-ca2d9a1a93fc.webp","image_position":"left","image_width":40,"title":"Lossless speech technology for smooth wireless voice recording","title_size_desktop":23,"title_size_mobile":18,"color_heading":"#4d4d4f","content":"<p>Uncompressed wireless recording enables free movement and pacing whilst working. You can easily move up to 5 meters or 16 feet away from your workstation and your recordings are safely transmitted to your computer in highest quality, without any interruptions. The cutting edge technology ensures every word is captured from the moment you press record.<\/p>","text_size_desktop":15,"text_size_mobile":14,"color_text":"#4d4d4f","button_text":"","button_link":"","show_separator":true,"color_title":"#eaeaea","image_gap":0}}},"block_order":["c6d1e0d8-3dbf-41d2-8f35-2b2d239ebbe4"],"settings":{"show_section_margin":false,"top-margin-desktop":30,"bottom-margin-desktop":30,"top-margin-mobile":20,"bottom-margin-mobile":20,"show_section_top_margin":false,"section-top-margin-desktop":80,"section-top-margin-mobile":50}},"49ebd1d1-6137-4361-9b7c-d